description.value: Inspect, test, sort, sample, or weigh nonagricultural raw materials or processed, machined, fabricated, or assembled parts or products for defects, wear, and deviations from specifications. The majority of these workers use precision measuring instruments and complex test equipment.

job_tasks.value: High risk job tasks associated with this job: Generate latex dust in manufacturing latex products Generate plant bioaerosols processing or packing food products Grind, mix, or weigh dyes or apply dyes to textiles Handle agents that cause allergic contact dermatitis or contact urticaria
